  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST BURNING SKIES</h1><p></p><br><h1>Burning Skies Neon free for Rock 'N' Roll Defense Owners</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/c7ccfebf7c8d52e963cadb1b86a3fea6.avif?t=1762262438\" width=600 height=168 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><br>Rocked by an explosive soundtrack, choose your band, place your equipments and defend the Rock 'N' Roll from everyone and everything who try to pull it down, on a totally hardcore tower defense!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/e92c90ea18b14bce8811193e704aaa53.poster.avif?t=1762262438\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/e92c90ea18b14bce8811193e704aaa53.webm?t=1762262438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/e92c90ea18b14bce8811193e704aaa53.mp4?t=1762262438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rock 'N' Roll Defense, is a tower defense game, where you should protect the rock concert from minions who are trying to stop the party!<br></li><li>Think you strategy, to get 3 skulls in every one of the 40 stages.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/79388ea439f22a67bd6d836eb51a5689.poster.avif?t=1762262438\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/79388ea439f22a67bd6d836eb51a5689.webm?t=1762262438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/79388ea439f22a67bd6d836eb51a5689.mp4?t=1762262438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pop, country, dance and even the hell minions are tryin to stop Rock from the spotlight and it's your job to stop them.<br></li><li>Use strategy to get coins to place and upgrade the best speakers.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/fc2a372a37c764a15832cce96363e0a3.poster.avif?t=1762262438\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/fc2a372a37c764a15832cce96363e0a3.webm?t=1762262438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/fc2a372a37c764a15832cce96363e0a3.mp4?t=1762262438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 stages, 20 enemy types (4 bosses), 8 different speaker (tower) types.<br></li><li>10 music soundtrack by amazing artists, across multiple Rock 'N' Roll Styles (You can download it for free!)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<br>Rocked by an explosive soundtrack, choose your band, place your equipments and defend the Rock 'N' Roll from everyone and everything who try to pull it down, on a totally hardcore tower defense!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/e92c90ea18b14bce8811193e704aaa53.poster.avif?t=1762262438\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/e92c90ea18b14bce8811193e704aaa53.webm?t=1762262438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/e92c90ea18b14bce8811193e704aaa53.mp4?t=1762262438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rock 'N' Roll Defense, is a tower defense game, where you should protect the rock concert from minions who are trying to stop the party!<br></li><li>Think you strategy, to get 3 skulls in every one of the 40 stages.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/79388ea439f22a67bd6d836eb51a5689.poster.avif?t=1762262438\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/79388ea439f22a67bd6d836eb51a5689.webm?t=1762262438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/438480/extras/79388ea439f22a67bd6d836eb51a5689.mp4?t=1762262438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pop, country, dance and even the hell minions are tryin to stop Rock from the spotlight and it's your job to stop them.<br></li><li>Use strategy to get coins to place and upgrade the best speakers.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autopl